<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw ka Pathian, Ka thawnnak le ka ralhruang
 Nangmah cu, kan dawttuk, hringhran ko ) 4

[C1]
   Bawipa cu a ka huhphengtu, ka himnak lung
   A ka kham-tu Siangpahrang, Ka Pathian
   Ka bochanmi ka thazang,
   A ka vengtu le a ka, khamtu ka phaw
   Ka himnak Lungpi fek a si.</lyrics>
<title>A HMUNMI PATHIAN</title>
</song>